---
title: Chicken, Sweet Potato and Chickpea Rogan Josh with Green Beans, Flaked Almonds and Garlic Naan
description: Though rogan josh is traditionally made with lamb, this staple Kashmiri dish works just as well with beef, goat, chicken or even vegetables! The sauce is aromatic and rich, spiced with ground coriander, cumin, paprika and turmeric.
